## Critical Success Factors

1. **60/40 Rule**: 60% pain point description + 40% product introduction = highest engagement
2. **3 Specific Questions** > generic invitations
3. **Author Reply Rate > 80%** = key to success
4. **Real > Perfect**: Vulnerability = strength
5. **First 4 Hours**: Check every 30 minutes, reply to EVERY comment

